@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_noizvy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v0
    tmp = wp.cos((0.64 * 0.23))
    v1 = (v0 * 0.19)
    v0 = wp.abs((0.12 * wp.exp(tmp + 0.70)))
    v0 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.46 / v1 + 0.33) - v2))
    data[tid] = v0
